&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>How to link old and new IDs when migrating data from one table to another</title><link>https://l-lin.github.io/post/2018/2018-03-29-postgresql_insert_and_link_ids/</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 Mar 2018 11:25:34 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://l-lin.github.io/post/2018/2018-03-29-postgresql_insert_and_link_ids/</guid><description>&lt;p>When proceeding a database migration, I often had to create a temporary table that will contains
the data from the old database.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>However, after the migration, I still need to have links between the old IDs and the new IDs for
